channel.title: Shop Error! Need someone to help code
channel.description: Hi. I am teaching myself to code but can't get everything to work. I am currently trying to add shops and everytime i add a shop there is an error when i try to run my server and will not let me log into the server with any account. I need a coder who could help me with this and code in the shops while also fixing the error. If anyone can help then please comment. Kind Regards, Getting Icy

item.title: Shop Error! Need someone to help code
item.dc:creator: @Funny_Man Funny Man
item.description:
@Funny_Man wrote:

Ix Soulcist xI:

It sounds like me to that you have a space problem in the Autospawn.Cfg if you created another npc for a shop.

Yeah… He Probably Didn’t Click (Tab) For His Spaces…

Note: Everytime you use a .cfg file… Your spaces need to be make with (tab)
